      "id": 10,
      "title": "Soil Moisture",
      "description": "Resistive sensor on A5. Dry calibration: 1023 ADC (air), wet: 800 ADC (submerged). NaN when pin is floating (sensor disconnected). Drift detection uses two rapid reads; if they differ by >50 ADC counts the sensor is declared absent.",
